From f24db279f8d05b2a9c919c673b7856bebca7c5b5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Manus AI <axiom@manus.ai>
Date: Wed, 15 Apr 2026 05:32:54 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] feat: strengthen Axiom to Tacto-level robustness

Bug Fixes (62 TypeScript errors resolved across 16 files):
- command-center.tsx: Fixed untyped agent result.data with proper generic types
- auth.ts & app/actions/auth.ts: Fixed unknown error type in catch blocks
- goods-receipts.ts: Added explicit return type to fix union type property access
- transactions/page.tsx: Fixed null-unsafe Date constructor calls
- risk-intelligence-view.tsx: Fixed number|null type mismatch
- admin/scenarios/page.tsx: Resolved duplicate ScenarioResult type conflict
- admin/ecosystem/page.tsx: Fixed undefined vs null state mismatch + arithmetic on optional
- admin/risk/page.tsx: Fixed RiskSupplier type mapping with explicit cast
- docs/page.tsx: Fixed possibly undefined diagram access with non-null assertion
- db/apply-migration.ts, check-parts.ts, verify-schema.ts: Fixed implicit any types
- ai-recommendations.ts, invoices.ts: Fixed SQL namespace type annotation

New Features:
- /inventory: Full Inventory Management page (stock levels, ABC classification, reorder alerts)
- /sustainability: ESG & Sustainability page (Scope 1/2/3 carbon tracking, ESG leaderboard,
  conflict minerals compliance, modern slavery statements, ISO certifications)

Aesthetic & UI Enhancements:
- sidebar.tsx: Redesigned with section dividers, visual hierarchy, AI features highlight,
  system status footer, Sustainability nav link
- login/page.tsx: Premium split-panel design with animated gradient, feature highlights
- header.tsx: Polished header with improved user avatar and layout
- globals.css: Added premium utility classes (badge-success/warning/danger), card hover
  effects, gradient animations, improved scrollbar styling
- axiom-logo.tsx: Refined SVG logo design
